<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>- وَلَا يَعُودُ مَرِيضًا، وَلَا يَشْهَدُ جَنَازَةً إِلَّا بِشَرْطٍ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>-<span style="color:#006d98"> وَيَبْطُلُ:</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span style="color:#707070">[١]</span> بِالخُرُوجِ مِنَ المَسْجِدِ لِغَيْرِ عُذْرٍ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span style="color:#707070">[٢]</span> وَبِنِيَّةِ الخُرُوجِ؛ وَلَوْ لَمْ يَخْرُجْ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span style="color:#707070">[٣]</span> وَبِالوَطْءِ فِي الفَرْجِ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span style="color:#707070">[٤]</span> وَبِالإِنْزَالِ بِالمُبَاشَرَةِ دُونَ الفَرْجِ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span style="color:#707070">[٥]</span> وَبِالرِّدَّةِ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span style="color:#707070">[٦]</span> وَبِالسُّكْرِ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>-<span style="color:#006d98"> وَحَيْثُ بَطَلَ:</span><a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>- وَجَبَ اسْتِئْنَافُ المُتَتَابِعِ غَيْرِ المُقَيَّدِ بِزَمَنٍ، وَلَا كَفَّارَةَ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>-<span style="color:#006d98"> وَإِنْ كَانَ مُقَيَّدًا بِزَمَنٍ مُعَيَّنٍ:</span><a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>أ) اسْتَأْنَفَهُ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>ب) وَعَلَيْهِ كَفَّارَةُ يَمِينٍ؛ لِفَوَاتِ المَحَلِّ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>-<span style="color:#006d98"> وَلَا يَبْطُلُ إِنْ خَرَجَ مِنَ المَسْجِدِ:</span><a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span style="color:#707070">[١]</span> لِبَوْلٍ، أَوْ غَائِطٍ، أَوْ إِتْيَانٍ بِمَأْكَلٍ وَمَشْرَبٍ.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span><span style="color:#707070">[٢]</span> أَوْ لِجُمُعَةٍ تَلْزَمُهُ، أَوْ طَهَارَةٍ وَاجِبَةٍ، وَنَحْوِ ذَلِكَ.<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>